article.headline: Antwi-Boasiako scores 30, Stephen F. Austin tops Utah Tech 84-71
article.description: — Nana Antwi-Boasiako scored 30 points to lead Stephen F. Austin to an 84-71 victory over Utah Tech on Saturday.
article.linkText: Antwi-Boasiako scores 30, Stephen F. Austin tops Utah Tech 84-71
article.story: HUNTSVILLE, Texas -- — Nana Antwi-Boasiako scored 30 points to lead Stephen F. Austin to an 84-71 victory over Utah Tech on Saturday. Antwi-Boasiako shot 8 for 11 from the floor, including 4 for 5 from 3-point range, and 10 for 12 from the free-throw line for the Lumberjacks (17-14, 10-10 Western Athletic Conference). Latrell Jossell added 20 points. AJ Cajuste totaled seven points, eight assists and four steals. Jaylen Searles led the Trailblazers (11-20, 7-13) with 19 points. Noa Gonsalves added 10 points and Larry Olayinka scored nine. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
